snippet.title: Super Mario Galaxy 2: Master Mode Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After 5 months and 27 crashes, SMG2 Master Mode is finally out ! This hack edits every level to make them harder. Test your skill and collect 76 stars in your journey. Good luck !

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Download link (most recent): https://www.mediafire.com/file/w2y8bpjnu499jcg/SMG2+Master+Mode+1.3.1.3.zip/file
Alt download link (most recent):
https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/707609774950318121/1205036864684429344/SMG2_Master_Mode_1.3.1.3.zip
Discord server: https://discord.gg/qhBqjPjJTK
Mod Logo: made by Aurelienbkt#8034

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Editing software: Shotcut
Capture Card: Elgato HD60 Pro
Thumbnail: made by Dante71#6861 ("TheYellowSquid" on youtube)
Huge thanks to him for also helping me edit that video
